    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Georgia\"\nformat:\n  html:\n    css: styles.css\n    embed-resources: TRUE\n    code-fold: true\n    page-layout: full\n    fig_caption: yes\n---\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n::: less-narrow-section\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n<div id=\"highlight-text\" style=\"padding-left: .9em; padding-right: 1em;\">18,701</div>\n<div id=\"highlight-text\" style=\"padding-left: 2.2em; padding-right: 2.4em;\">10,107</div>\n<div style=\"display: block; &#10;              padding-left: 1em; &#10;              padding-right: 1em; &#10;              color: #ff6400; &#10;              font-size: 1.25em; &#10;              font-family: Graphik; &#10;              font-weight: bold; &#10;              text-align: center;\">Highly<br>Indeterminate</div>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center; justify-content: center; \">\n<div id=\"bold-text\" style=\"padding-left: 5em; padding-right: 5em;\">Currently Eligible for<br>Parole but in Prison</div>\n<div id=\"bold-text\" style=\"padding-left: 5em; padding-right: 5em;\">Eligible for Parole in<br>the next 1-5 years</div>\n<div id=\"bold-text\" style=\"padding-left: 5em; padding-right: 5em;\">\n<span class=\"tippy html-widget html-fill-item-overflow-hidden html-fill-item\" height=\"338px\" id=\"htmlwidget-e970a60fa0f1219d662e\" width=\"100%\"></span>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-e970a60fa0f1219d662e\">{\"x\":{\"opts\":{\"placement\":\"bottom\",\"flip\":true,\"theme\":\"light\",\"content\":\"To compare the degrees of indeterminacy, or unpredictability\\n   of time served, of prison-sentencing systems of different jurisdictions,\\n   we use a qualitative ranking framework based on the Robina Institute's\\n   Prison-release Discretion And Prison Population Size Report.<br><br>\\n   <b>High indeterminacy:<\\/b> More than 60-80 percent indeterminacy (first prospect of\\n   release at 20-39.99 percent of judicial maximum)\"},\"text\":\"Prison Sentencing<br>System&#9432;\"},\"evals\":[],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n</div>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n::: \n\n<br>\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<style type=\"text/css\">.nav-tabs {justify-content: center;}</style>\n```\n:::\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"tabbable\">\n<ul class=\"nav nav-tabs shiny-tab-input\" id=\"tabsetpanel\" data-tabsetid=\"1895\">\n<li class=\"active\">\n<a href=\"#tab-1895-1\" data-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" data-value=\"Overview\">Overview</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"#tab-1895-2\" data-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" data-value=\"Parole Eligibility\">Parole Eligibility</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"#tab-1895-3\" data-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" data-value=\"Releases from Prison\">Releases from Prison</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"#tab-1895-4\" data-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" data-value=\"Disparities\">Disparities</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tab-content\" data-tabsetid=\"1895\">\n<div class=\"tab-pane active\" data-value=\"Overview\" id=\"tab-1895-1\">\n<br/>\n<div id=\"line-graph\">\n<div class=\"highchart html-widget html-fill-item-overflow-hidden html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-e0451e8a1b91abd6fdb9\" style=\"width:100%;height:500px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-e0451e8a1b91abd6fdb9\">{\"x\":{\"hc_opts\":{\"chart\":{\"reflow\":true,\"width\":500,\"height\":400},\"title\":{\"text\":\"Trends in Prison Population, Releases to Parole, and Parole Eligibility\"},\"yAxis\":{\"title\":{\"text\":null},\"labels\":{\"format\":\"{value:,.0f}\"}},\"credits\":{\"enabled\":false},\"exporting\":{\"enabled\":false},\"boost\":{\"enabled\":false},\"plotOptions\":{\"series\":{\"label\":{\"enabled\":false},\"turboThreshold\":0},\"treemap\":{\"layout